Class MainController

java.lang.Object
com.example.cs213_cafe_project.MainController
public class MainController extends Object
This class is the controller for StoreFrontView.fxml Creates and sets the stages for all the other views in RUCafe Project Contains all the universal data objects that are needed to successfully run the project.
